Package org.jlab.icalibrate.swing.worker

Provides the iCalibrate Swing worker classes.

Workers are executed in a background thread.

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BeamEstablishedLookupWorker
    This is a SwingWorker which verifies that beam has been established to the selected hall by checking the hall current monitor.
    CreateNewDatasetWorker
    This is a SwingWorker which performs the data gathering work for ion chamber calibration.
    IonChamberLookupWorker
    This is a SwingWorker which looks up the ion chambers for the selected hall.
    LaserLookupWorker
    This is a SwingWorker which looks up the injector laser in use for the selected hall.
    MinimumExecutionSwingWorker<T,​V>
    This is a SwingWorker which guarantees that it will take at least a minimum amount of time to do its job.
    PassLookupWorker
    This is a SwingWorker which looks up the pass in use for the selected hall.
    TargetLookupWorker
    This is a SwingWorker which looks up the target in use for the selected hall.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CreateNewDatasetWorker.WorkerState
    The state of the worker.
